Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.75,Chiha-poem,,0000,0000,0000,,As I wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:05.65,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We touched it at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.44,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But it was on my side, so I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.11,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.78,trot,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Trit-Trot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:10.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:11.65,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,It was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.65,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I was faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:14.91,trot,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Trit-Trot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:14.91,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:16.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.57,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.33,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I was slightly faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:20.58,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,...is contesting a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.51,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.98,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of this team is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.44,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The person who can make \Neveryone happy is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.59,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will challenge the Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:32.97,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.60,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up the card she contested,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.85,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but that makes up for the earlier one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:42.05,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.62,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just be your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Time to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.15,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.19,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:54.70,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.37,Chiha-overlap,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:56.45,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time!
