Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.70,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, this is no simple \Nletter of remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:37.89,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,It's a work of literature!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.25,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,It deserves to be published!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.07,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Stop reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.82,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,This is better than Kawabata \NYasunari and Natsume Soseki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.73,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.14,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you leaving, Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying here as \Npart of my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.77,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave until the \Ntournament's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.73,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You ooze integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.14,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Brings tears to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.67,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Once my uniform is dry, I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.21,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.60,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Coach!  Tajiri!  You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.69,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Way too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:08.73,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.61,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,The engine stalled just when we got \Nclose, and we had to call JAF.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.36,Chiha-main,Taj,0000,0000,0000,,Since we knew we were disqualified,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.50,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we stopped for gyudon on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.30,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.00,Chiha-main,Taj,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that Queen Wakamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.26,Chiha-main,Taj,0000,0000,0000,,It's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.02,Chiha-main,Taj,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you skinny now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:22.95,Chiha-main,Taj,0000,0000,0000,,What diet did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.96,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,Tajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.07,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the results downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.02,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Shoyo from Kyoto is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.02,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,They lost to Mizusawa from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.57,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.25,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been \Nthere for their match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.02,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.03,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa won?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:39.99,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Are they still in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:45.79,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa beat Shoyo to \Nmake the top four,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:48.95,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're playing First Akashi Girls' \Nfrom Hyogo in the semi-finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.54,Chiha-main,Nog,0000,0000,0000,,An impressive run for an unknown school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.53,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,They're winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.02,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,They're playing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.05,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi...  Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.64,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Team matches are so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.30,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Like a fun type of recreation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:12.02,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to do things together, \Nkaruta or otherwise.
