Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You're incredible, Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:50.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
