Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.71,Chiha-flashback,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Or they believe that a \N"The" card will be read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.02,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Superstitions...
