Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.44,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,but he's already formed \Nhis own superstitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.12,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun is learning...
